items.text: bowled him! length ball, Ervine comes forward and pushes at it, the ball turns just a little bit but enough to beat the bat, the sound of timber. Zimbabwe five down for 100
items.shortText: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Ervine, OUT

dismissal.text: CR Ervine  b Mehidy Hasan Miraz 24 (48b 1x4 0x6) SR: 50.00

items.preText: Peter Moor is the new batsman

items.text: fuller and worked past the non-striker, the ball dives across, collides with the non-striker, but fails to stop the ball. The bat drops from Williams' hand and he completes the single without the bat

items.text: length ball, comes forward and pushes, gets beaten on the inside edge, Mushfiqur too fails to collect. Mushfiqur gathers the throw and flicks the ball through his leg but Moor was back home

items.text: fuller on pads, Moor sweeps it fine, past short fine leg for four
